data.horoscope_data: The next few months will encourage you to be flexible as you forge your own path now that Neptune is in Aries and your career zone. While you can obtain a dream job or dream reputation, you don’t need to follow the road map so closely, Cancer. Take a few risks now. They might pay off down the road.Start by expanding your mind when Mars in your sign trines Saturn in Pisces on Friday. You’re eager to see the world through fresh eyes, so this is a great time to plan a grand trip or study something new.You’re ending the week on a romantic note as Venus in Pisces trines Mars on Sunday. This is a great time to level up relationships and expand your friend group. You can learn more about the world through the connections you make.
